### Mengantar API — REST client file
# Kompatibel dengan VS Code REST Client, JetBrains HTTP Client, dan editor sejenis.
# Isi variabel di bawah (atau pakai file env editor-mu). @key RAHASIA — jangan commit nilai asli.
# Endpoint TULIS ditandai [WRITE] — jalankan hanya di sandbox.

@base = https://api-public.mengantar.com
@key = GANTI_DENGAN_API_KEY
@prefix = {{base}}/api/public/{{key}}

# Isi setelah menjalankan request pencarian/list di bawah:
@originId = ORIGIN_ID
@destId = DEST_ID
@timeId = TIME_ID
@batchId = BATCH_ID

### 1. Validasi key (estimate dummy)
GET {{prefix}}/order/estimate?origin_id=5fc62f63f8f44b34aa4c0e0a&destination_id=5fc62de8f8f44b34aa4bdc58&courier=all&weight=1

### 2. Cari data wilayah → ambil data[]._id
GET {{prefix}}/address/search?keyword=menteng

### 3. List alamat pickup (origin) → ambil data[]._id
GET {{prefix}}/address

### 4. [WRITE] Buat / update alamat pickup
POST {{prefix}}/address
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

PICKUP_AUTOFILL={{destId}}&PICKUP_ADDRESS=Jl. Contoh No. 1&PICKUP_PIC_PHONE=08123456789&PICKUP_PIC=Budi&PICKUP_NAME=Gudang Utama

### 5. List jadwal pickup
GET {{prefix}}/time?address={{originId}}

### 6. [WRITE] Tambah jadwal pickup — date = mm-dd-yyyy, time = 9:00..18:00
POST {{prefix}}/time
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

address_id={{originId}}&date=07-10-2026&time=13:00

### 7. Estimasi ongkir (semua kurir)
GET {{prefix}}/order/estimate?origin_id={{originId}}&destination_id={{destId}}&courier=all&weight=2

### 8. Estimasi + COD (COD_AMOUNT huruf besar)
GET {{prefix}}/order/estimate?origin_id={{originId}}&destination_id={{destId}}&courier=JNE&weight=2&COD_AMOUNT=150000

### 9. Estimasi public (flat 20%) — TANPA prefix key
GET {{base}}/api/order/allEstimatePublic?origin_id={{originId}}&destination_id={{destId}}&weight=2

### 10. Estimasi 3PL (harga standar) — TANPA prefix key
GET {{base}}/api/order/allEstimate3PL?origin_id={{originId}}&destination_id={{destId}}&weight=2

### 11. Skor performa kurir (kirim allEstimateData dari #7)
POST {{prefix}}/order/getPerformancePublic
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{ "city": "JAKARTA PUSAT", "allEstimateData": {} }

### 12. Invoice & saldo
GET {{prefix}}/invoices

### 13. Assignee (untuk orders.assignee)
GET {{prefix}}/my-users

### 14. [WRITE] Buat shipment — resi di data[].cnote_no. JT/Ninja/SiCepat: jangan paralel!
POST {{prefix}}/order
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "courier": "JNE",
  "pickup": { "type": "scheduledPickup", "address_id": "{{originId}}", "time_id": "{{timeId}}", "volume": "volumeMobil" },
  "orders": [{
    "customerAddressDataId": "{{destId}}",
    "customerAddress": "Jl. Tujuan No. 5, Bandung, Jawa Barat 40123",
    "customerName": "Siti", "customerPhone": "08111111111",
    "parcelContent": "Kaos katun", "weight": 2, "quantity": 1, "goodsValue": 150000
  }]
}

### 15. [WRITE] Bayar order unpaid
POST {{prefix}}/order/pay-unpaid
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

courier=JNE&batch_id={{batchId}}

### 16. Lacak order by order_id
GET {{prefix}}/order?order_id=ORDER_ID

### 17. List order (filter)
GET {{prefix}}/order?page=1&size=50&courier=JNE&cod=NON_COD&category=collected_customer

### 18. [WRITE] Hapus order
DELETE {{prefix}}/order
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

courier=JNE&ids=["ORDER_OBJECT_ID"]

### 19. List batch
GET {{prefix}}/batch?page=1&size=50&courier=JNE

### 20. [WRITE] Hapus batch
DELETE {{prefix}}/batch
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

courier=JNE&id={{batchId}}

### 21. Skor penerima (cek risiko RTS sebelum COD)
GET {{prefix}}/getReceiverScoreByNumberUser?search=8123456789
